title: Kaunas Airport (EYKA) gets a makeover!
description:
Kaunas International Airport (EYKA) has recently been updated in MSFS, enhancing the overall experience. The update includes not only the airside but also the passenger drop-off area, featuring new traffic signs and additional improvements.
